name: aws-secretsmanager-jdbc 1.0.7 Release
body: Version increases for com.fasterxml.jackson.core, aws-java-sdk-secretsmanager, aws-secretsmanager-caching-java, and aws-secretsmanager-jdbc.

name: aws-secretsmanager-jdbc 1.0.6 Release
body: Merged pull request to allow support for VPC endpoint override via the config file

name: aws-secretsmanager-jdbc 1.0.4 Release
body:
Updated dependency versions for 
1. jackson
2. aws-secretsmanager-cache

name: aws-secretsmanager-jdbc 1.0.3 Release
body: Publishing to new sonatype endpoint for aws

name: aws-secretsmanager-jdbc 1.0.2 Release
body:
This release contains the following changes:
* Add support for MariaDB
* For MySQL, check for com.mysql.cj.jdbc.Driver in class path and fall back to com.mysql.jdbc.Driver
* Change JSON parsing error message to be more generic

name: aws-secretsmanager-jdbc 1.0.1 Release
body:
* Fixed an issue with the way JDBC URLs are handled:
   * acceptsURL() now returns false if the URL is a JDBC URL that does not begin with jdbc-secretsmanager
   * connect() returns null if the URL parameter is not one we accept
* Updated jackson-databind dependency to 2.8.11.1

name: aws-secretsmanager-jdbc 1.0.0 Release
body: Initial release of the AWS Secrets Manager library of JDBC drivers
